</entry><entry><id>491d698e6b149e69dcf661c561bed0ff</id><title>🆘🆘蝕讓成交｜持貨15年貶值12% 外區客筍價1235萬購薄扶林貝沙灣套2房</title><updated>2025-08-14T12:01:45+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T12:01:45+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595568"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595568"&gt;大家記住mark低吹反彈班人卜街&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="62" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_o05.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3993408%2F%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25EF%25BD%259C%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%25B2%25A815%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B2%25B6%25E5%2580%25BC12-%2520%2520%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%25AD%258D%25E5%2583%25B91235%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%2596%2584%25E6%2589%25B6%25E6%259E%2597%25E8%25B2%259D%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%25A5%25972%25E6%2588%25BF%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=b4ac2ce012106c0f2a597632c3c179aa&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3993 ... 薄扶林貝沙灣套2房?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;利嘉閣地產貝沙灣分行-D組高級經理雷敏儀稱，該行促成薄扶林貝沙灣6期1座低層A室成交，實用面積約733方呎，採2房1套間隔，可眺望海景。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;新買家為外區租客，早前經利嘉閣真盤源平台搵樓，見上述放盤即約代理睇樓。客人認為現時租金高企，息口回落正是入市的好時機，加上心儀單位景觀優美，能眺望海景，屋苑附近環境清幽，即決定洽購。業主原以1,550萬元放售，議價後以低市價1,235萬元成交，折合實用面積呎價約16,849元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;據悉，原業主在2010年以約1,399.9萬元買入單位。持貨15年貶值164.9萬元或12%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;[&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; 本帖最後由 叔叔要不要 於 2025-8-14 17:51 編輯 &lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007007&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=2037002220689e475326e7f1_37366317"/><published>2025-08-14T12:01:45+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>439e0fa026c01e55a64818edfd704d46</id><title>🆘🆘直擊單位｜滙景花園3房小海景賣880萬 回到10年前跌價2%</title><updated>2025-08-14T12:02:23+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T12:02:23+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595580"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595580"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3992913%2F%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25EF%25BD%259C%25E6%25BB%2599%25E6%2599%25AF%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%25923%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%2599%25AF%25E8%25B3%25A3880%25E8%2590%25AC%2520%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%2588%25B010%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%25B7%258C%25E5%2583%25B92-%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=69d56de61bd173a59f8aea7f665a3839&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3992 ... 到10年前跌價2-?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;港鐵藍田站滙景花園有持貨10年業主，帳面微蝕離場。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;市場消息指，17座低層E室，實用720平方呎，屬套3房戶型，外望小海景，最新以880萬元易手，呎價12,222元。較上星期17座高層H室，同呎價，享開揚海景，以890萬元成交。最新成交價僅低10萬元，故屬理想水平。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;▼點擊圖片放大&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;+4&lt;br/&gt;原業主於2015年以898萬元購入，持貨10年，帳面損失18萬元或2%。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007008&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=2037002220689e475326e7f1_37366317"/><published>2025-08-14T12:02:23+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>d5b79640efabcb8fa9a8a4ccbc2ba210</id><title>請驗樓師驗收惠州新盤遭多名保安恐嚇！😱😱😱難怪不少內地人都寧可來港置業</title><updated>2025-08-14T12:24:16+08:00</updated><author><name>stoddort</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T12:24:16+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595811"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595811"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #0000ff; "&gt;好多年過30嘅廢中佬冇本事買香港樓&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="9" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/titter.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #0000ff; "&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=3434944" target="_blank"&gt;@~kurapika~&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7321592" target="_blank"&gt;@過去深愛的羊腩&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7333091" target="_blank"&gt;@vovovo.N&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7256576" target="_blank"&gt;@叔叔要不要&lt;/a&gt;分身Account&lt;a class="usertag" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=3395993" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span uid="3395993"&gt;@Youngbro&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7327835" target="_blank"&gt;@買樓唔好搞阿叔&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=6673014" target="_blank"&gt;@袋中紅色主題&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=6577149" target="_blank"&gt;@車站宇宙的婆仔&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=4338023" target="_blank"&gt;@smart004&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7320360" target="_blank"&gt;@新窮A&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="usertag" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=3697327" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span uid="3697327"&gt;@hkduck123&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="usertag" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=5503647" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span uid="5503647"&gt;@931931&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="usertag" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7348949" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span uid="7348949"&gt;@johnlamAust2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/120825_169_iet_fish__v1_1024.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/120825_169_iet_fish__v1_1024.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/2b6ffd/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/120825_169_iet_fish__v1_1024.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;▲網絡熱話｜本港年輕情侶請驗樓師驗收惠州新盤遭多名保安恐嚇！ 網民：唔敢想像入去住之後有咩事發生&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;隨著近年中港加快融合，不少港人均於內地置業。日前有一對95後香港情侶於抖音上載影片；指自己早前購入惠州星河冠譽府一夥3房單位，並於日前前赴惠州收樓，並請來驗樓師幫忙驗收單位。惟驗收期間，一名身穿紅色上衣的男子及屋苑多名保安上門，恐嚇業主及該名驗樓師，最終更需請公安上門處理。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121615_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121615_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/aabd54/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121615_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121620_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121620_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/f3ddab/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121620_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121629_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121629_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/652d67/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121629_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;女事主對相關行為感到憤怒，直言自己合法合規地請驗樓師上門驗收單位，卻被多名人士上門欺負及恐嚇，認為相當恐怖，亦反問現時聘用驗樓師驗樓是否犯法。驗樓師更向他們反映，要不是兩名業主在場，可能已被抓至後樓梯打了。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121842_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121842_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/3d65e7/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121842_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121904_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121904_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/e8d689/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121904_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121908_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121908_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/63b124/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121908_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;相關片段日前被轉載至本港討論區，有網民直言，「驗樓都咁誇張，唔敢諗入去 (住) 之後有咩事發生」，「未入伙已食鐵拳」；故難怪不少內地人都寧可來港置業，皆因「起碼法律保障及管理好過大陸N倍」。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007022&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=2037002220689e475326e7f1_37366317"/><published>2025-08-14T12:24:16+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>aba00f9ca1e5511cb1c6a6f11aedc1c2</id><title>🔥🔥🔥收租廠佬大受刺激！以全蝕姿態連沽各區8住宅 平均虧近3成😆😆😆</title><updated>2025-08-14T12:25:35+08:00</updated><author><name>johnlamAust2</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T12:25:35+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595826"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595826"&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YwCcKXURXro?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://youtu.be/YwCcKXURXro?si=f1DtNjyHM3jTu30G" target="_blank"&gt;https://youtu.be/YwCcKXURXro?si=f1DtNjyHM3jTu30G&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007023&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=2037002220689e475326e7f1_37366317"/><published>2025-08-14T12:25:35+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>3eeb2417a10bce108715bb0a0ecefd93</id><title>香港根本上係荒山野嶺。</title><updated>2025-08-14T17:17:17+08:00</updated><author><name>我要真發達復活</name></author><content type="html">&lt;